zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532405\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532405\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 24, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tlc1665702735327.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tlc1665702735327.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tlc1665702735327.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tlc1665702735327\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      unicode\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enable or disable Unicode support in the SYB connector.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__section_pgc_vww_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961156e51\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__p_d60095e1_d60096e1_d60097e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unicode</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__section_jrf_www_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961156e65\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__p_d60101e1_d60102e1_d60103e1\">When the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unicode</span> option is specified,\n        Unicode characters can be used in fields with wide-character packing codes. By default, this\n        is limited to characters in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP).</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__note_xcv_www_jcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If you need to support the full Unicode range, you\n        should also set the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">smp</span> connector option.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__p_d60104e1_d60105e1_d60106e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unicode</span> option is not\n        specified, Unicode support is disabled. In this case wide-character packing codes are mapped\n        to C packing codes; for example, a W10 field is mapped to C40 (to accommodate the extra bits\n        required for Unicode).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__section_ot3_xww_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961156e89\">Example: Enabling Unicode Support</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tlc1665702735327__pre_ld4_yww_jcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">usys$syb_params charset utf8, unicode, smp, keyword</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyw1665702963805.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>smp</a><p>When Unicode support is enabled, allow the full range of Unicode characters to be stored in W packing code fields.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/adh1665702963734.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Support for Unicode in the SYB Connector</a><p>The Uniface SYB connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Unicode</a><p>Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgd1665702875492.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Wide Character Packing Code (W)</a><p>The W (wide character) packing code is used for Unicode characters.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532405\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532405\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "unicode Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 24, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 unicode Enable or disable Unicode support in the SYB connector. Syntax USYS$SYB_PARAMS unicode Description When the unicode option is specified, Unicode characters can be used in fields with wide-character packing codes. By default, this is limited to characters in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). Note: If you need to support the full Unicode range, you should also set the smp connector option. If the unicode option is not specified, Unicode support is disabled. In this case wide-character packing codes are mapped to C packing codes; for example, a W10 field is mapped to C40 (to accommodate the extra bits required for Unicode). Example: Enabling Unicode Support usys$syb_params charset utf8, unicode, smp, keyword Copy Related Links smp When Unicode support is enabled, allow the full range of Unicode characters to be stored in W packing code fields. Support for Unicode in the SYB Connector The Uniface SYB connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled. Unicode Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers. Wide Character Packing Code (W) The W (wide character) packing code is used for Unicode characters. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}